# Petri Dish Pro Roadmap

## v0.3 - Organism Gate
- Download-controlled evolution script, not a patch script stored inside the repo.
- Fixed PowerShell parser wound.
- Organism Gate menu, Python sim core, Electron HUD, receipts, tests.

## v0.4 - Biology Kernels
- Chemotaxis, biofilm matrix, dormancy/reactivation, mutation, antibiotic resistance transitions, predator/prey refinements.

## v0.5 - Scientific Artifacts
- Parameter sweeps, run comparison, CSV/SVG/PNG exports, reproducibility hash, validation scorecard.

## v0.6 - Standards Adapters
- CSV import/export schema, SBML/CellML adapter design, AnnData/h5ad design, COMBINE/OMEX provenance design.

## v0.7 - NexusGate Candidate
- Lane integration, authority boundaries, receipts, human-authorized promotion only.

## v1.0 - Governed Scientific Sandbox
- Stable experiment schema, plugin manifest, artifact bundle, validation scorecard, and claim boundary.
